Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:06.10,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:08.49,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Imanity's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:10.23,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:11.36,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,After that grand entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:14.64,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:16.80,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect it to be set in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:18.05,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:19.17,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's our home, but we're the away team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:21.58,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,We can't help you, so I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:26.53,ngnl-overlap,T,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your world, Masters?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:22.84,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,but please handle this yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:24.01,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.89,0:00:32.57,ngnl-narration,T,0000,0000,0000,,You were incredibly popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.57,0:00:37.93,ngnl-narration,T,0000,0000,0000,,You were so popular that girls from \Nall around the world chased you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:45.89,ngnl-narration,T,0000,0000,0000,,But in your heart, there \Nis only one woman you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:52.75,ngnl-narration,T,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:58.56,ngnl-narration,T,0000,0000,0000,,if faced with too many temptations, \Nyour love will waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.38,0:01:02.10,ngnl-narration,T,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make it through all the temptations
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.10,0:01:06.41,ngnl-narration,T,0000,0000,0000,,and convey your feelings to the one you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:10.88,ngnl-narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Living or Dead Series Side Story:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:19.41,ngnl-narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Love or Loved 2: Hit Her \NWith Your Bullet of Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:49.59,ngnl-main,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Living or Dead Series Side Story:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.03,0:01:52.38,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Love or Loved 2:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:55.44,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit Her With Your Bullet of Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:04.89,ngnl-ep-title,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(1000,400)}Killing Giant
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.28,0:02:05.00,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:07.41,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the world inside the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.74,0:02:12.77,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be holding the game \Ninside this fictional field.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:13.54,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:14.40,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.85,0:02:16.11,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let me confirm something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:19.22,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fictional place. \NIt doesn't really exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:23.15,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's a virtual world \Nyou imagined for your game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:25.42,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.99,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:30.29,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:32.75,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That brought all kinds of trauma back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.05,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make misleading stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.88,ngnl-overlap,In,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:36.84,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.83,ngnl-overlap,In,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a problem with the level?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:38.90,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:40.57,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell would you \Nuse this for a level?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:41.83,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is this psychological warfare?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:42.94,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to screw with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.35,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,This is a science fiction level very popular
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.82,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,with the youth of the Eastern Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:49.68,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the only reason it was chosen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.68,0:02:51.48,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:56.24,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,It's a game, so to an extent, you will be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:00.73,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,That explains why I can be out in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:06.49,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro! Calm down! This isn't Tokyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:09.34,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,It only looks like it! They just imagined it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:13.00,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This is a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:16.25,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,just like Pers*na, or Stein's \NG*te, or Akiba Str*p!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.88,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,If we're in a game, we're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:21.88,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Inside a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.06,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:31.70,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.16,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:39.03,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,Then, everyone, I shall explain the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.27,0:03:42.40,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,First, look at the box at your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:52.21,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,You'll use those guns to shoot \Nthe NPCs who chase you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.18,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,We're shooting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:54.78,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,By shooting them at times,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.60,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,and exploding them at times,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:58.25,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,you will make them fall in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.18,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that G*l Gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.60,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,The girls who fall in love with you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:04.19,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,will give you their love power and disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:10.19,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,The ammo fired from the love-love \Ngun is your own love power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.74,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is called the love-love gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:13.73,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:19.53,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,However, if Izuna shoots one of you, \Nyou'll turn into her love slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:20.09,ngnl-main-top,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Izuna-tan Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:20.97,together,In,0000,0000,0000,,Izuna-tan\NLove <3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.97,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you say, "you'll join her side"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.27,0:04:24.25,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,As girls all over the world \Nturn to look your way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:28.11,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,the one person you love will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:32.04,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,Conveying your love power to \Nmake her fall in love with you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:34.12,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is the goal of this game!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:36.99,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,That ends the explanation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:42.57,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, I just have \Nto reject every girl I see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.00,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Who do I think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:46.90,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Izuna wants \Nthe harem ending where
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.32,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,all four of us fall for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.64,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,but we're after her only.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:52.00,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:59.60,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,One last note: magic cannot be used \Nin the virtual world, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:00.75,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:03.51,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need a further detailed \Nexplanation of the rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:06.07,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll figure them out as I play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.46,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:13.94,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,Firing the love-love gun \Ndepletes your love power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:18.65,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,Defeating NPCs restores your love power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:24.56,ngnl-main-top,S,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on? This is too creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:23.80,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,If an NPC touches you, \Nyour love power depletes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:27.31,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,and if it runs out, the NPCs \Nwill stop approaching you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:29.89,ngnl-main-top,S,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:32.31,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll run out of energy \Nto fire your love-love gun
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:35.05,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,and become unable to continue combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.82,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,So what happens if you \Nshoot an ally, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:42.04,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,You can restore love power \Nto an ally who has run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:47.57,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,You can also save companions who have \Nbeen turned into Izuna's love slaves,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:51.04,ngnl-main,In,0000,0000,0000,,but the one shot temporarily becomes \Na love slave of the one who shot—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:56.20,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.68,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:00.55,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea such a cute, beautiful girl
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.55,0:06:02.54,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,was so close to me this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:07.78,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,My blindness makes me \Nwant to gouge out my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:10.75,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,No, Brother, we're sibli—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:14.09,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Jibril!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:15.21,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:16.14,ngnl-main-top,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.96,ngnl-main-top,S,0000,0000,0000,,Are you rejecting your brother's love?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:21.03,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the "love triangle" and "NTR" \NI saw in my master's books!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.96,0:06:21.03,ngnl-main-top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro! My beloved Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:25.76,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even possess the emotion of love, \Nbut somehow it excites me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:30.13,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Jibril, you'll be punished later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:32.71,ngnl-main-top,J,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, forgive me, Shiro-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:32.25,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:33.97,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're a love slave,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:35.79,ngnl-main-top,J,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hold back my curiosity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:37.56,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,you lose all functions and can't control yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.56,0:06:39.54,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:42.38,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You all left me on my own again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:43.42,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's horribl—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.16,0:06:45.78,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! My prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:48.04,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Steph, do you understand the rules so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.04,0:06:50.29,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Love doesn't need rules!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:52.91,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I don't know them, our love is eternal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.92,ngnl-overlap,S,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.04,0:06:55.98,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,So put this here, and this here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:54.55,ngnl-overlap,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:57.30,ngnl-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart is pounding...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:57.43,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Now pull your index finger in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:58.96,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What am I—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:03.72,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so beau-ti-ful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:06.95,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so. It bounces off of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.86,ngnl-main-top,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let myself go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:09.60,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,This bouncing ability is the key, Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.58,ngnl-main-top,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:10.58,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:14.46,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Also, even though we're in a game,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:17.05,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,our stamina doesn't change \Nmuch from real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:19.50,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your running to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:20.45,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:21.93,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.29,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,let's go, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:32.46,ngnl-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's finally getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.49,ngnl-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see it, Fi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:37.30,ngnl-internal,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Coming in loud and clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:41.46,ngnl-internal,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'm borrowing your eyes, Kurami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:46.44,ngnl-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,The Warbeasts must hate this magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.85,ngnl-internal,F,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to maintain this spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:55.62,ngnl-internal,F,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm doing it for you, Kurami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.53,ngnl-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,The Warbeasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:03.01,ngnl-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,Their physical abilities are said to \Napproach the limits of physics itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:06.76,ngnl-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how you fight a race like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:13.32,ngnl-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,Show me, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.64,ngnl-flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Izuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:28.51,ngnl-flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,When's the last time you \Nthought a game was fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.34,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:48.10,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.97,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes this game special!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:51.88,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:55.80,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Target: NPC's cotton panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:57.24,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Cotton max thickness: 1 millimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.11,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,12 o' clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.67,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance: 20050.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:00.66,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Firing angle: 93.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.32,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,300 meters per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:04.49,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,Acceptable targeting error: within 0.5 millimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.22,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.22,0:09:06.92,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.33,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:22.20,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.17,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I failed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:25.59,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:27.51,ngnl-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,I give up on this race.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:28.91,ngnl-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,They're a bunch of morons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:35.22,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you having fun, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.10,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose, many people will be unhappy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:39.98,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,so you have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:42.36,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,But if you win, your opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:44.10,ngnl-main-top,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Bra destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.76,ngnl-main-top,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hand bra for the win!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:50.67,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I've never thought it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.49,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,These footsteps...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.52,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:11.65,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,She's coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.13,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro, you're mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.64,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,I missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:35.68,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.09,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:45.29,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:51.52,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're surprised right now, Izuna-tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:55.79,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,In the genre called FPS, where the \Nbest shooters in the world gather,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:59.38,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the one who holds all the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.71,0:11:02.83,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:06.14,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:12.84,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,Her terrifying calculation abilities allow \Nher to grasp her enemies' movements,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:17.04,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,and her firing intervals and \Ndodges take into account
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:18.98,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,everything from her understanding of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:21.01,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,your movement patterns to \Nhow fast you can fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.56,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,almost verging on precognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:25.93,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like your bullets are \Npassing right through her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:29.53,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,and hers are tracking you \Nlike guided missiles, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:33.53,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,This is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:40.40,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,I have to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.25,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:56.02,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:58.32,ngnl-main,I,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Flugel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:00.42,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jibril!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:03.46,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,A bomb to blind her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:09.78,ngnl-main,I,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:14.06,ngnl-main,I,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... I can't fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:15.84,ngnl-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Jibril!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:34.85,ngnl-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,I can't dodge it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:53.09,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:58.11,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,My master, please come back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:01.10,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:04.75,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,She can use her clothes as a shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:09.12,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.43,ngnl-overlap,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,The kings are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:10.85,ngnl-main,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Imanity is winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:14.06,ngnl-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that, Fi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:16.69,ngnl-internal,K,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. I saw it through your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:21.49,ngnl-internal,K,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro-san's firing skills are amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.49,0:13:23.22,ngnl-internal,K,0000,0000,0000,,but more amazing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:25.47,ngnl-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I can't believe she was able
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:28.95,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,to sense and dodge Sora's shot \Nbefore it was even fired,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:32.31,ngnl-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,when he was so far away \Nand completely silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.07,ngnl-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:38.47,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,This is the sixth sense of \Nthe Warbeasts, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:40.17,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.38,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a sixth sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:43.74,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's seeing the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:44.49,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.89,0:13:47.22,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:49.49,ngnl-internal,F,0000,0000,0000,,A cheat code. They're cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:52.15,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a con game!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:54.89,ngnl-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,I see. A cheat you can't prove.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:58.66,ngnl-internal,C,0000,0000,0000,,If they say it's a sixth sense, \Nthere's nothing you can prove.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:02.80,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,So they did know this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.88,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,More than we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.32,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:09.07,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,Izuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.56,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the corridor below you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:14.68,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro is exhausted and can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:16.99,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,Take them out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:18.95,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to tell me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:23.43,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what little tricks they may have,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.25,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way they can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:41.44,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,So now we're finally on the defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.40,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:43.52,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:45.32,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't able to finish \Nthis during the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.55,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,so now we'll have to wing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:49.21,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:51.94,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,We're trying to play a fair \Ngame against cheaters
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:54.50,ngnl-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,who know the game inside and out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:56.25,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.81,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Your luck just ran out, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:02.55,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting you back for all you've \Ndone to me, and for Izuna-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:08.55,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean, Jibril-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:10.90,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go? You left me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:11.99,ngnl-overlap,S,0000,0000,0000,,Bringing her was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:12.63,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.51,0:15:26.64,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:30.28,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,And my heart is pounding so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:36.50,ngnl-flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,When's the last time you \Nthought a game was fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:40.29,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.41,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro-sama, what's our next strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.41,0:15:46.71,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Jibril, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:50.43,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Master, maybe this really is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.06,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Even for Shiro-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:53.44,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, she can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:56.80,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,If there's something I can't \Ndo in a game, Shiro can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:16:00.00,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's always been true, and it always will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.31,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:06.33,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.82,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Has your brother ever doubted you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.73,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.66,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,It's
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.70,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,your turn now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:22.88,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.04,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,No—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:33.57,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.35,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:57.21,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:02.54,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand why Shiro-sama \Nprotected you, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:04.17,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:06.85,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I do, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.85,0:17:09.60,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that Shiro couldn't find the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.54,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}was{\i0} the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:14.16,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,It was blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.75,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:19.25,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Everything, including Shiro joining \Nthe enemy's side, is Blank's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:23.26,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's up to me to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:27.49,ngnl-main,,0000,0000,0000,,complete the magic formula that \Nwill lead us to the promised victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:30.63,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, isn't it, Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.00,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Jibril.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:35.03,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Fight Izuna to buy me time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:39.33,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:42.77,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind if I defeat her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:45.54,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:47.87,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I might as well tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:49.66,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's a death flag, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:50.89,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:54.66,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just go defeat her normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:01.90,ngnl-main,J,0000,0000,0000,,That makes this easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:07.97,ngnl-main,I,0000,0000,0000,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:14.40,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there, puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:18.39,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I feel I'm experiencing déjà vu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:22.98,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,The last time I challenged the \NEastern Federation and lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:26.12,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,were you my opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:31.36,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Master told me to buy time, \Nbut since I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:33.67,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,let's have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:36.30,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Throw every cheat you've got at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:40.17,ngnl-main,T,0000,0000,0000,,and embarrass yourself to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:57.35,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:59.98,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,Going to a different area isn't going to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:02.75,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell am I supposed to do, Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.06,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I need to run to the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:17.96,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's planned for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:19.83,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, she'll catch up to me soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:24.00,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:28.21,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't Shiro running after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:31.02,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,If she were running, she'd have any \Nnumber of chances to defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:36.15,ngnl-flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your running to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:36.95,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:40.89,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't I the one who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.00,0:19:45.59,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,If I get this wrong, it's going to be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.87,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,But, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.78,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Shiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:00.60,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother's just about had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:04.61,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is a rough game for a guy \Nwho never leaves his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:16.12,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother can't make a mistake now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:23.74,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:27.41,ngnl-internal,S,0000,0000,0000,,if there's something you would \Nnever expect, it's that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:37.30,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,...I wouldn't try to dodge at all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:45.08,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:47.96,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.68,ngnl-main,I,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Izuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:54.46,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,That took way too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:08.10,ngnl-main,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,This is why you saved your strength \Nand didn't run, right, Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:10.91,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:12.64,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:16.36,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,Sora just shot her.\NShe shouldn't be able to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:20.66,ngnl-internal,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,My panties are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:22.50,ngnl-main,I,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:27.00,ngnl-main,I,0000,0000,0000,,Was it really only her panties that got hit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:29.26,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,You finally figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:33.60,ngnl-main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro was never on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:39.27,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,She let the shot hit her clothes and \Npretended to be under my control!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:40.99,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,They fooled me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:43.20,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:46.02,ngnl-internal,I,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:55.22,ngnl-flashbackinternal,S,0000,0000,0000,,When's the last time you \Nthought a game was fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:08.77,ngnl-main,I,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.02,0:23:46.04,ngnl-next-ep-title,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Rule Number 10
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.70,0:23:44.74,ngnl-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there!\NGive your power to Blank!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.74,0:23:46.04,ngnl-main-top,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!
